OL,3,CBergerac writer hopes reboot will
OL,4,Creplicate success of original drama
OL,6,FThe lead writer and executive producer
OL,7,Fof Jersey crime drama Bergerac says he
OL,8,Fhopes that the programme can run for
OL,9,Fmany series after it was revived by
OL,10,FBritish broadcaster UKTV.
OL,12,FToby Whithouse is most famous for
OL,13,Fcreating BBC supernatural show Being
OL,14,FHuman and has also written several
OL,15,FDoctor Who episodes.
OL,17,FNow he is the showrunner responsible
OL,18,Ffor bringing back the popular
OL,19,FDetective Sergeant Jim Bergerac for an
OL,20,Finitial six episodes on U&DRAMA and
OL,21,Fonline streaming service U.
