OL,6,FA host of stars have signed up for the
OL,7,Freboot including Damien Molony, Zoe
OL,8,FWanamaker and Philip Glenister.
OL,10,FToby explains: "It's really exciting
OL,11,Fthat we're going to be moving forward
OL,12,Fwith this incredible cast, it's
OL,13,Fthrilling.
OL,15,F"When we talked to Phil Glenister
OL,16,Fabout doing the show, he was in the
OL,17,Flast ever episode of the original
OL,18,Fseries and another thing that struck
OL,19,Fus was the reverence in which the
OL,20,Fpeople of Jersey hold the original
OL,21,Fshow.
