OL,6,F"We're very mindful of that and it's a
OL,7,Fbig responsibility, it's part of
OL,8,FJersey culture. Hopefully, we're not
OL,9,Fgoing to offend or upset anyone."
OL,11,FAddressing concerns that some of the
OL,12,Fshow is being shot in the UK, Toby
OL,13,Fexplains: "Of course we have to keep
OL,14,FJersey at the absolute heart of the
OL,15,Fshow so we're going to film there as
OL,16,Fmuch as possibly can.
