OL,6,F"A lot of these things are dependent
OL,7,Fon budget and the availability of
OL,8,Flocation and crew. As the series moves
OL,9,Fforward and hopefully we go into a
OL,10,Fsecond, third, fourth and fifth
OL,11,Fseason, the plan is to gradually build
OL,12,Fup an infrastructure on Jersey.
OL,14,F"I've been several times in
OL,15,Fpreparation for the show and it's a
OL,16,Fbeautiful island, the people have been
OL,17,Fincredibly friendly and I think it's
OL,18,Fgoing to be a real delight to work
OL,19,Fthere."
