OL,3,CBergerac writer hopes reboot will
OL,4,Creplicate success of original drama
OL,6,FIt is more than 30 years since
OL,7,FBergerac was last filmed and it is
OL,8,Fhoped this latest series will keep the
OL,9,Fprogramme's essence while being
OL,10,Fsuitable for a contemporary audience.
OL,12,FToby adds: "The original show was very
OL,13,Fmuch a product of its time, we've
OL,14,Fobviously looked back at the original
OL,15,Fshow but I think that has to be done
OL,16,Fwith some caution.
OL,18,F"So much has changed in how we consume
OL,19,Ftelevision and stories so we have to
OL,20,Freflect that and move with the times."
