OL,6,FOne of those changes sees Zoe's
OL,7,Fcharacter Charlie Hungerford change
OL,8,Fgender having previously been played
OL,9,Fby a man.
OL,11,FToby explains: "We felt we wanted to
OL,12,Fhave more of an equal balance between
OL,13,Fmale and female representation in the
OL,14,Fshow.
OL,16,F"It would look a little odd now if the
OL,17,Fbalance is skewed now as much as it
OL,18,Fwas so it was something we wanted to
OL,19,Faddress."
