OL,6,FHowever, key elements of Bergerac's
OL,7,Fidentity will run through to the new
OL,8,Fseries.
OL,10,FToby says: "There are elements of the
OL,11,Fmain character I really want to hang
OL,12,Fonto so Bergerac's struggle with
OL,13,Falcoholism, I felt that was something
OL,14,Fthat is timeless in a way and how he
OL,15,Fmanages to maintain his work and
OL,16,Fobligations."
